// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0352 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: ec3596f3-643e-5f72-a355-a7ddd5597d76

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
